													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Yonas (Harper 3) is moving wide of the group, an arrow notched to his bow, eyes fixed on the player. He's straying further from the Harpers' torches, walking along a sharp incline where road falls away, toeing the line between shadow and light."
